oulette Roulette is another popular casino game you can play online. The game is played on a 38 numbers wheel colored black or red and you only need to predict where a ball will land after spinning the wheel. There are several types of bets you can wager on the roulette wheel, with the simplest being predicting whether the ball will land on a black or red piece. You can also bet on specific numbers, but that significantly lowers your odds. Craps Craps is a classic table game played with dice. One person plays as a “shooter”, whose responsibility is to roll the dice. The other players wager on the dice outcome. However, the shooter wins when they get eleven or seven on the first roll. When the shooter rolls other numbers, it becomes the “point”. The shooter then has to match this number before rolling a seven to claim the win. The other players on the table can place different bets and the simplest option is to predict whether the shooter wins or loses. Another bet that craps players can place in an online casino is predicting whether the shooter hits another number before rolling a seven. Every bet is only good for the next roll.